reviewText: Very fun and entertaning LA BLUE GIRL is a great anime. Definetly for adults and for those who like tentacle hentai.
box is incorrect. Cover art is digitized but back looks ok. No art inside. But cd quality is great so its ok.

The Box art depicts tentacle hentai but there is only one short scene with tentacles.  Each volume, 5 & 6, is about 30 minutes and thats average for hentai DVD's.  If you prefer hentai with lots of plot and martial arts, this may be perfect for you.  If you prefer more tentcle hentai and sex and can settle for less plot look at the "night evil falls" volumes.
